description:
As a user I want to select Visitors
    So I purchase the right ticket
name: Select Visitors

steps.name: I am a user of ForSea
I visit the Booking page
the 'Sweden, Helsingborg' and 'Denmark, Elsinor' fields are populated on the To and From field
I select "Car under 6 meter" from the vehicle modal
I click the "Visitors" field in the Booking Page
I should see "Select Visitors" modal in Booking page
I click adult "1" button on the modal
I click "Done" button from the modal
The 'Book your journey' heading is displayed on the top left hand side
